item.title: HTB: Meow
item.description: Introduction I have performed my first HackTheBox machine called “Meow”, this is of course a starting point box allowing me to get used to using these machines and how they work. I will also be using my own machine to hack these boxes. My current machine is running Parrot OS on VMware. Firstly we must answer a couple of questions before we hack this machine. Task 1 The first answer is Virtual Machine.
